title: Y'ra at Dawn
info:
From the module :
[quote]This is my contribution to the multichannel music-competition in ASM'95. All samples were sampled by me from my Ensoniq TS-10 and some CD's, with the exception of samples 4, 13-20, 23, 25, 26 and 30, which were more or less ripped from [artist]1670[/artist], [artist]595[/artist], [artist]711[/artist] and [artist]669[/artist].[/quote]
